FBIS4-16260 "drsov073_m_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-073 Daily Report 15 Apr 1994 Tajikistan Post of President To Be Instituted Under New Constitution Post of President To Be Instituted Under New Constitution LD1504083094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0700 GMT 15 Apr 94 LD1504083094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] The post of president will be instituted in Tajikistan. This is the first result of the work of the commission of the Republic's Supreme Soviet to draft a new constitution for Tajikistan. The draft constitution with a presidential form of government will be put to a nationwide referendum.
